  <brief_title>Dexmedetomidine in Pediatric Tonsillectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dose Response Relationship of Dexmedetomidine in Decreasing Post Operative Analgesic Requirements in the Pediatric Tonsillectomy Patient</official_title>
  <sponsors>
